---
import Base from '~/layouts/Base.astro';

const jsonLd = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Person',
  name: '정채상',
  url: 'https://ieumtech.net/ko/about',
  jobTitle: '대표, 이음 테크',
  sameAs: 'https://linkedin.com/in/chaesang',
  worksFor: { '@type': 'Organization', name: 'Ieum Tech' },
  alumniOf: [{ '@type': 'CollegeOrUniversity', name: '서울대학교' }],
};
---
<Base
  title="정채상 소개 — 이음 테크"
  description="정채상 — 엔지니어링 리더. 혼돈에서 구조를 만들어 온 ex-Google 13년의 기록."
  lang="ko"
  path="/ko/about"
  ogType="profile"
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
  altLangPath="/about"
>
  <style slot="head" is:inline>
    .hero-label { margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .profile-headline { line-height: inherit; margin-top: 0; }
    .highlights-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
    .highlight-card { text-align: center; padding: 20px 12px; }
    .highlight-number { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-accent); letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1.2; }
    .highlight-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); font-weight: 400; margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.4; }
    @media (max-width: 480px) { .highlights-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
    .simple-list { gap: 14px; }
    .simple-list-item .label { font-weight: 600; }
    .simple-list-item .detail { font-weight: 400; }
    .see-more { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .see-more a { color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .see-more a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>

  <main>
    <section class="about-section" id="about" style="border-top: none; padding-top: 56px;">
      <div class="about-inner">

        <div class="about-profile">
          <div class="profile-avatar"><img src="/profile.jpg" alt="정채상" width="96" height="96" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div>
            <h1 class="profile-name">정채상</h1>
            <p class="profile-secondary-name">Chaesang Jung</p>
            <p class="profile-headline">기술이 지나온 자리에 늘 사람이 있었습니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-summary">
          <ul>
            <li>임베디드, 검색, 커머스, 핀테크, 클라우드, 산업 AI</li>
            <li>실리콘밸리 13년, 한국에서의 그 앞뒤</li>
            <li>엔지니어, 매니저, VP, CTO, 자문으로 옮겨 다닌 자리들</li>
            <li>잘 풀린 프로젝트, 자연스레 접힌 프로젝트</li>
            <li>여전히 배우는 자리에서, 가끔 먼저 본 것을 건넵니다.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="about-block">
          <h2>함께 일한 사람들의 말</h2>
          <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px;">
            <blockquote style="margin: 0; padding: 0 0 0 16px; border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent);">
              <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-text); font-style: italic; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 8px;">"Chaesang well-balances his technical expertise with the depth of his product domain knowledge, which stems from his immense care for the users he serves. His care and empathy for his reports as a manager — thinking of how to help people grow in their careers."</p>
              <cite style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--color-muted); font-style: normal;">— Jennifer Lin, ex-Engineering Director, Google (managed Chaesang for 3 years)</cite>
            </blockquote>
            <blockquote style="margin: 0; padding: 0 0 0 16px; border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent);">
              <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-text); font-style: italic; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 8px;">"What sets Chaesang apart is his dedication to the learning and growth of his colleagues. His presence in the workplace provided us with a sense of psychological safety — we knew there was always someone to listen."</p>
              <cite style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--color-muted); font-style: normal;">— Ada Suhkyung Kim, UX Research & AI Product Lead</cite>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-block">
          <h2>더 보기</h2>
          <ul class="see-more">
            <li><a href="/ko/companies">거쳐 온 자리들 →</a></li>
            <li><a href="/ko/projects">함께 했던 프로젝트들 →</a></li>
            <li><a href="/ko/talks">남긴 말과 글들 →</a></li>
            <li><a href="/ko/writing">글 →</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="about-block">
          <h2>학력</h2>
          <div class="simple-list">
            <div class="simple-list-item"><span class="label">서울대학교</span><span class="detail">— 공학 석사, 컴퓨터공학</span></div>
            <div class="simple-list-item"><span class="label">서울대학교</span><span class="detail">— 공학 학사, 컴퓨터공학</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-block">
          <h2>미국 특허</h2>
          <div class="simple-list">
            <div class="simple-list-item"><span class="detail">Ranking of presentation modes for particular content (US9146972)</span></div>
            <div class="simple-list-item"><span class="detail">Indexing application pages of native applications (US9002821B2)</span></div>
            <div class="simple-list-item"><span class="detail">Automatically implementing an application in response to a search query (US9524347B1)</span></div>
            <div class="simple-list-item"><span class="detail">Triggering and ranking of native applications (US9514195B2)</span></div>
            <div class="simple-list-item"><span class="detail">Ranking of native application content (US8996520B2)</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <section class="cta-section" id="contact" aria-labelledby="cta-heading">
    <div class="cta-inner">
      <h2 class="cta-heading" id="cta-heading">여기 어딘가에서 질문이 생겼다면, 이쪽으로 이어 주세요.</h2>
      <p class="cta-sub">정리되지 않은 질문이어도 괜찮습니다.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="mailto:hello@ieumtech.net" class="btn">이메일</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/chaesang" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
